text: The fish tengiri sambal was super delicious and other than that dish can eat for hungry not for taste

The food tasted average. There were not much choices of food although it was 1pm (lunch time). Half white rice, one vege and one piece of sambal chicken costed rm 12. A bit pricy for the average food.
Beware of this restaurant, I got food poisoning and stomach flu because of their leftover dhall curry (Sambar). The worst ever restaurant in my life. Its overpriced too
Just because sg is nearby doesnt mean that can charge high, first time tried the food here and ofc will be the last though! Such a tastless food, so pricey !! Such a bad experience :(

This restaurant has a lot of food and all the food is delicious 😋😋
Reasonable price and good service
Highly recommended, MUST TRY 👍👍👍
